@daboss2003/capacitor-image-marker
==================================

This Capacitor plugin is a from-scratch port of the API surface of
react-native-image-marker (https://github.com/JimmyDaddy/react-native-image-marker)
by jimmydaddy, which is also distributed under the MIT License. No source code
from the original project is included; this package reimplements the public API
for the Capacitor platform.

